url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-qX","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":32947,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/28\/no-barrier-allah-dawatan\/","url_meta":{"origin":1671,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Nothing to block two supplications","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTwo supplications have no barrier between them and Allah: the supplication of the oppressed, and the supplication of a man for his brother behind his back.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 11232 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33850,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/12\/23\/angels-jinn-insan\/","url_meta":{"origin":1671,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Creation: Allah created angels, jinn, and humankind","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe angels were created from light, the jinn were created from a mixture of fire, and Adam was created as has been described for you.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2996 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32245,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/17\/allah-loves-most-others\/","url_meta":{"origin":1671,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Love: Allah loves most those who love others","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 17, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo two men love each other for the sake of Allah, behind their backs, but that the most beloved of them to Allah has the strongest love for his companion.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 5424 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3351,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/06\/02\/opening-dua-qiyam-al-layl\/","url_meta":{"origin":1671,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet&#8217;s first supplication for night prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would stand for prayer at night, he would begin by saying, \u201cO Allah, the Lord of Gabriel, Michael, and Israfel, Originator of the heavens and the earth, Knower of the unseen and the seen, You judge between\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15419,"url":"https:\/\/www.